00:01:45.345 --> 00:01:46.695
To get them thinking.

00:01:47.245 --> 00:01:52.455
They want the right to vote, but I want to get them thinking…it’s not just gender

00:01:52.505 --> 00:02:00.425
equality, it’s eating a plant-based diet, LGBTQ rights, racial equality, anti-capitalism…”

00:02:01.675 --> 00:02:04.295
I couldn’t finish before Bobby interrupted.

00:02:05.575 --> 00:02:11.855
